name: Female tongues and mouths
description:
Female tongues and mouths

Model intended to generate more realistic tongues and mouths.

Can produce mouths and tongues of any shapes or sizes, photorealistic if desired. Given the appropriate prompt, long tongues from likely human to anything.

Trained on SD 1.5, tested with models Deliberate and Dreamshaper

Provided samples include base SD 1.5 model, Deliberate and Dreamshaper. These are RAW samples that have not been improved with GFPGAN or CodeFormer. Provided samples of realistic output, fantasy, humongous, etc.

Triggers: tongue, tongue out, mouth open

More samples on https://www.deviantart.com/znort2005

modelVersions.name: Female tongues and mouths v2
modelVersions.description:
Features:

  • Reduced the number of unwanted artifacts

  • Improved consistency

Training:

  • 2k selected images

  • 20k steps, batch size 4

  • Learning rate 5e-5:2000, 5e-6:10000, 5e-7:20000

  • Hypernet structure 1,4,1

  • Hardware AWS R5g.xlarge

  • Duration 24h
